{"status": "VERIFIED", "cf_tracking_firefox60": "---", "cf_tracking_firefox61": "---", "classification": "Client Software", "creator": "ehsan@mozilla.com", "cc": ["camelia.badau@softvision.ro", "dao+bmo@mozilla.com", "jan@ikenmeyer.eu", "jaws@mozilla.com", "jhofmann@mozilla.com", "magicp.jp@gmail.com", "mcastelluccio@mozilla.com", "ntim.bugs@gmail.com", "richard.marti@gmail.com", "ryanvm@gmail.com"], "depends_on": [1462635], "creation_time": "2018-05-04T22:12:53Z", "cf_user_story": "", "cf_tracking_firefox_relnote": "---", "platform": "Unspecified", "keywords": ["regression"], "summary": "mixed content blocking warning is displayed as gray on the dark theme", "cf_last_resolved": "2018-05-27T13:07:38Z", "attachments": [{"creator": "ehsan@mozilla.com", "is_obsolete": 0, "is_patch": 0, "flags": [], "content_type": "image/png", "id": 8973348}, {"creator": "ehsan@mozilla.com", "is_obsolete": 0, "is_patch": 0, "flags": [], "content_type": "image/png", "id": 8973351}, {"creator": "dao+bmo@mozilla.com", "is_obsolete": 0, "is_patch": 0, "flags": [{"status": "+", "name": "review", "modification_date": "2018-05-27T09:48:12Z", "type_id": 748, "creation_date": "2018-05-27T09:00:39Z", "id": 1762203, "setter": "ntim.bugs@gmail.com"}, {"status": "+", "name": "approval-mozilla-beta", "modification_date": "2018-05-28T01:56:42Z", "type_id": 721, "creation_date": "2018-05-27T18:10:56Z", "id": 1762260, "setter": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}], "content_type": "text/x-review-board-request", "id": 8980953}], "assigned_to_detail": {"email": "dao+bmo@mozilla.com", "id": 219124, "name": "dao+bmo@mozilla.com", "real_name": "D\u00e3o Gottwald [::dao]"}, "severity": "normal", "is_confirmed": true, "is_creator_accessible": true, "cf_has_regression_range": "---", "comment_count": 14, "comments": [{"text": "Created attachment 8973348\nmixed-content-blocking.png\n\nPlease see the screenshot attached, captured on aurora.", "author": "ehsan@mozilla.com", "id": 13255922, "time": "2018-05-04T22:12:53Z"}, {"text": "Created attachment 8973351\nmixed-content-blocking.png\n\nBTW if you click on the \"Show connection details\" arrow, the other mixed content blocking text is also displayed as gray.", "author": "ehsan@mozilla.com", "id": 13255929, "time": "2018-05-04T22:14:13Z"}, {"text": "So we're using Graytext all over the identity popup, but I agree it's a bit dark on the dark theme. Does anyone know a good cross-theme alternative to Graytext for the identity popup or do we need to special-case dark theme here? Would also be interesting for bug 1457512 in which it's planned to make more sections gray...", "author": "jhofmann@mozilla.com", "id": 13259402, "time": "2018-05-07T12:38:17Z"}, {"text": "(In reply to Johann Hofmann [:johannh] from comment #2)\n> Does anyone know a good cross-theme alternative to\n> Graytext for the identity popup or do we need to special-case dark theme\n> here?\n\n--autocomplete-popup-secondary-color could be renamed and moved from ThemeVariableMap.jsm to LightweightThemeConsumer.jsm to be available for all popups.", "author": "dao+bmo@mozilla.com", "id": 13265104, "time": "2018-05-09T11:54:46Z"}, {"text": "Bug 1462635 did not fix this.", "author": "dao+bmo@mozilla.com", "id": 13366433, "time": "2018-05-27T08:56:09Z"}, {"text": "Created attachment 8980953\nBug 1459352 - Fix disabled text color in webext theme styled control center.\n\nReview commit: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/247104/diff/#index_header\nSee other reviews: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/247104/", "author": "dao+bmo@mozilla.com", "id": 13366436, "time": "2018-05-27T09:00:39Z"}, {"text": "Comment on attachment 8980953\nBug 1459352 - Fix disabled text color in webext theme styled control center.\n\nhttps://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/247104/#review253178", "author": "ntim.bugs@gmail.com", "id": 13366446, "time": "2018-05-27T09:48:12Z"}, {"text": "Pushed by ntim.bugs@gmail.com:\nhttps://hg.mozilla.org/integration/autoland/rev/9ca472c1e19a\nFix disabled text color in webext theme styled control center. r=ntim", "author": "pulsebot@bots.tld", "id": 13366447, "time": "2018-05-27T09:49:43Z"}, {"text": "https://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-central/rev/9ca472c1e19a", "author": "csabou@mozilla.com", "id": 13366557, "time": "2018-05-27T13:07:38Z"}, {"text": "https://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-central/rev/9ca472c1e19a", "author": "csabou@mozilla.com", "id": 13366562, "time": "2018-05-27T13:07:54Z"}, {"text": "Comment on attachment 8980953\nBug 1459352 - Fix disabled text color in webext theme styled control center.\n\nApproval Request Comment\n[Feature/Bug causing the regression]: Bug 1408121\n[User impact if declined]: see comment 0\n[Is this code covered by automated tests?]: no, css change not covered by tests\n[Has the fix been verified in Nightly?]: \n[Needs manual test from QE? If yes, steps to reproduce]: see comment 0\n[List of other uplifts needed for the feature/fix]: bug 1462635 (which was just uplifted)\n[Is the change risky?]: low risk\n[Why is the change risky/not risky?]: css only\n[String changes made/needed]: n/a", "author": "ntim.bugs@gmail.com", "id": 13366727, "time": "2018-05-27T18:10:56Z"}, {"text": "Comment on attachment 8980953\nBug 1459352 - Fix disabled text color in webext theme styled control center.\n\nFix for difficult to see text with the dark theme. Approved for 61.0b9.", "author": "ryanvm@gmail.com", "id": 13368327, "time": "2018-05-28T01:56:42Z"}, {"text": "https://hg.mozilla.org/releases/mozilla-beta/rev/17fdd7dd7ba3", "author": "aiakab@mozilla.com", "id": 13368740, "time": "2018-05-28T09:18:37Z"}, {"text": "Verified fixed on Windows 7 x64, Windows 10 x64, Ubuntu 16.04 x64 and macOS 10.13 using Firefox 61 Beta 9 (buildID: 20180528091514) and latest Nightly 62.0a1 (2018-05-29).", "author": "camelia.badau@softvision.ro", "id": 13370902, "time": "2018-05-29T12:45:29Z"}], "id": 1459352, "priority": "P2", "mentors_detail": [], "cf_crash_signature": "", "version": "unspecified", "cf_qa_whiteboard": "", "cf_tracking_firefox_esr52": 